aliens.name: Four Arms
aliens.description: A hulking, four-armed alien with incredible strength from the planet Khoros.
weaknesses: Large size makes him an easy target

aliens.name: Heatblast
aliens.description: A magma-based life form that can generate and control fire.

aliens.name: XLR8
aliens.description: A velociraptor-like alien with incredible speed capabilities.

aliens.name: Diamondhead
aliens.description: A silicon-based life form made of super-hard green crystals.

aliens.name: Upgrade
aliens.description: A biomechanical alien that can merge with and upgrade any technology.

aliens.name: Grey Matter
aliens.description: A tiny frog-like alien with extraordinary intelligence.

aliens.name: Stinkfly
aliens.description: A large insectoid alien capable of flight and slime attacks.

aliens.name: Ripjaws
aliens.description: An anglerfish-like alien adapted for aquatic environments.

aliens.name: Wildmutt
aliens.description: A dog-like alien with no eyes but powerful sensory abilities.

aliens.name: Ghostfreak
aliens.description: A phantom-like alien with supernatural abilities.
weaknesses: Cannot possess beings with strong will

aliens.name: Cannonbolt
aliens.description: An armadillo-like alien that can roll into an indestructible sphere.

aliens.name: Wildvine
aliens.description: A plant-based alien with extensible vines and seed bombs.

aliens.name: Upchuck
aliens.description: An alien with multiple stomachs that can eat and convert any matter into energy.

aliens.name: Ditto
aliens.description: A small alien that can create unlimited copies of itself.
weaknesses: Clones cannot recombine if separated too far

aliens.name: Eye Guy
aliens.description: An alien covered in eyes that can fire various energy beams.
weaknesses: Blinding all eyes renders him powerless

aliens.name: Way Big
aliens.description: A colossal humanoid alien over 100 feet tall with cosmic powers.
weaknesses: Huge size makes him an easy target

aliens.name: Swampfire
aliens.description: A plant-like alien that can generate methane and control fire.

aliens.name: Echo Echo
aliens.description: A silicon-based alien that can duplicate and create powerful sonic attacks.

aliens.name: Humungousaur
aliens.description: A dinosaur-like alien that can grow larger and stronger.

aliens.name: Jetray
aliens.description: A manta ray-like alien capable of supersonic flight and space travel.

aliens.name: Big Chill
aliens.description: A moth-like alien that can freeze enemies and phase through matter.

aliens.name: Chromastone
aliens.description: A crystalline alien that can absorb and manipulate energy.
weaknesses: Overloading with energy can crack him

aliens.name: Brainstorm
aliens.description: A crustacean-like alien with extraordinary intelligence and electric powers.
weaknesses: Shell can be removed exposing brain

aliens.name: Spidermonkey

weaknesses: Can be trapped in own webs

aliens.name: Alien X
aliens.description: An omnipotent alien with near-unlimited cosmic powers.

aliens.name: Lodestar
aliens.description: A living magnet that can control metallic objects.

aliens.name: Rath
aliens.description: A tiger-like alien with incredible strength and an aggressive personality.

aliens.name: Water Hazard
aliens.description: An armored crustacean alien that can control and shoot water.

aliens.name: Ampfibian
aliens.description: A jellyfish-like alien that can generate electricity and phase through matter.

aliens.name: Armodrillo

aliens.name: Terraspin
aliens.description: A turtle-like alien that can generate powerful wind attacks.

aliens.name: NRG
aliens.description: A radioactive energy being contained in a protective suit.

aliens.name: Fasttrack
aliens.description: A feline-like alien with incredible running speed.

weaknesses: Cannot turn invisible if covered in substances

aliens.name: Eatle

aliens.name: Clockwork
aliens.description: A mechanical alien that can manipulate time itself.
weaknesses: Time powers don't work on Chronosapiens
